  "detailed_description": "Run, jump, slide, and flap your way through beautiful, hand-crafted worlds.<br><br>Toleo is designed to be fast, fluid, and fun!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312780/extras/c3a9436b3f2b8e88c0aa8ec27e09a18f.poster.avif?t=1689845515\" width=800 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312780/extras/c3a9436b3f2b8e88c0aa8ec27e09a18f.webm?t=1689845515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312780/extras/c3a9436b3f2b8e88c0aa8ec27e09a18f.mp4?t=1689845515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features: </strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play as pink or blue birdboy.<br></li><li>Jump, double-jump, drop-jump, bounce, slide, slide-jump, and double-slide-jump.<br></li><li>Die to hedgehogs, birds, spikes, turrets, lava, and more.<br></li><li>Cool cutscenes.<br></li><li>100 challenging levels in 10 unique worlds.<br></li><li>Lots of checkpoints.<br></li><li>Hard Mode with not a lot of checkpoints.<br></li><li>Speedrun Mode with on-screen timer and auto-skip cutscenes.<br></li><li>Amazing soundtrack by Tantrum Tech.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312780/extras/1e405b3ffa20b4c038d613433f68b260.poster.avif?t=1689845515\" width=640 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312780/extras/1e405b3ffa20b4c038d613433f68b260.webm?t=1689845515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312780/extras/1e405b3ffa20b4c038d613433f68b260.mp4?t=1689845515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
